### autosuggest
POST https://music.163.com/api/search/suggest/web
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8
Accept: application/json
Referer: http://music.163.com

s=depeche%20mode&limit=15

### get song details via ID
POST https://music.163.com/api/song/detail
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8
Accept: application/json
Referer: http://music.163.com

ids=%5B17976684%5D

